name: Julia / I Am Where
description:
Portrait of Julia.
From project "I am where"
The project about "Touched out syndrome". I ask young mothers where is the place on their bodies where they feel they are they, and where baby didn't touched them a lot.

Julia said: "I am where everything comes together in a single axis, where my frame is, where all the loads and pains are, where the hands transfer their efforts to the body."

4920  x  3766 px

2021
